```
 Clearly we Can see [3,6] is covererd
**Approach** 🚩 
1:-> First sort the arrary using Comparator.
2:-> Compartor will sort in the ascending , when start is same then sort finish in decending.
3:-> Put size of interval in ans variable.
4:-> Now take a count of max reach done at every interval, initialize with -1.
5:-> Traverse the vector, as start is sorted and start condition is covered already (IDEA-2) , We will check only Condition 2.
6:->Now if finish of curr vector is less than max reach ,So Inteval is covered=> decrease ans by one.
7:->if finish of curr vector is greater than maxreach, so Update the maxreach.
8:-> Return the ans.😃
